metadata.name: VENUSTAS
metadata.description:
The works in this collection explore the intersection of art and blockchain technology, as well as the powerful and evocative imagery of the Italian Baroque artist Caravaggio. The pieces in this collection aim to capture the intense and passionate emotions of Caravaggio's art while also incorporating the cutting-edge possibilities of blockchain.

At the same time, it celebrates the enduring power of the human imagination and the beauty of the natural world.
